Exit codes
----------
0 => the user 
1 => not a root or in the sudo group 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Main.sh
---------
The Start point of the script you can run it by using  ./Main.sh
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Validation.sh 
----------------
it contains the functions of check in the application :
a. the apache is installed in this machine or not
b.The virtual host the user choose to do actions on exist or not 
c.htpass file exists or not when the user want to add some authenticatios
d. the user is root or in the sudo group 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. ApacheControl.sh
-------------------
it contains the actions like:
a.install apache2
b.uninstall apache2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3.authentication.sh 
-------------------
it contains the actions like:
add authentication for a specific vertiual host
delete authentication from a specific vertiual host
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4.Vertiual host
---------------
check if Apache2 installed
if not installed echo to the user it's not installed and ask if he want to install 
add new virtual host
deleted vertiual host check if it exists
disable virtual host
enable virtual host
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5. Menu.sh
-----------
display main menu with different options
check if apache2 installed
if installed the user can got to virtual hosts menu by click 3
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
